addFriend(address,string).details: To simplify the code duplication of friends is not checked

addRestaurant(string).details: To simplify the code, duplication of restaurants isn't checked

doVote(uint256).details: To simplify the code duplicate votes by a friend is not checked

returns.validVote: Is the vote valid? A valid vote should be from a registered  friend to a registered restaurant
